ou spend a lot of time dragging arrows and boxes. This time would be better spend in thinking about &lt;em&gt;why&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;where&lt;/em&gt; to move your arrows and boxes.&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In addition, software that intermingles concept and representation typically is a vendor lock: You cannot (easily) get out if you find some more useful softare.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
